tags.note: RIP Taiko Supermarket. Your shopping carts have lived on.
To access by car use multi-level parking (NOT the south side parking, shopping carts cannot go out that way!). To enter by foot, use the mall entrance east of Loblaws and enter via the mall.
Signage says "Bloor Street Market, Home of President's Choice". Is really a Loblaws.
